---

LMDseq: RNA sequencing analysis pipeline for low input samples 
obtained through Laser Microdissection (LMD)

This pipeline implements methodology described in:
- Di Chiaro P, et al. "Mapping functional to morphological variation reveals 
  the basis of regional extracellular matrix subversion and nerve invasion 
  in pancreatic cancer." Cancer Cell 2024.
- Di Chiaro P, et al. "A framework to mine laser microdissection-based omics 
  data and uncover regulators of pancreatic cancer heterogeneity." 
  Gigascience 2025.

